('7118f140-1730-4777-8177-b324d8461e2e', '41916093-0efc-44ff-8e64-89c61ecc926c', 'f5302662-7b26-41b6-a78b-6dc771037323', 'Faced with this, this person blurts a number or an ultimatum, then has to live with wherever it lands, and true to form cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 'Lets urgency substitute for analysis, converting pressure directly into action. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A rush of adrenaline that narrows focus fast, resolving into guilt absorption — that leaves a residue of vigilance well past the event itself.', 0.49, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
