('6650f43e-e8b8-44c4-970c-8e2e8e7d731a', '18c2aab3-c8ee-46f0-9413-9a25cf9eeaa0', '405296ff-2f61-4f19-9cb5-c4534ab73309', 'Faced with this, this person leans into the move, adding exposure where others are flinching and betting on the reversal, and true to form sees malicious intent and exploit risk in every standard smart contract update.', 'Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, treating hesitation itself as evidence something is off. This time the variable is money moving in real time.', 'A noticeable but manageable spike of unease, resolving into aggressive counter — that fades within the hour once the decision is locked in.', 0.59, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
