('942a9198-36be-47d4-a3f7-a8cc452515f4', '653b971b-53ef-4aaa-9376-99133f235a19', '9c63e2a1-5292-4ca4-888c-dc9b62716ebc', 'Faced with this, this type lunges at the most visible fix, trading a fast intervention for a considered one, and true to form refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.', 'Prefers a decisive wrong turn to an open-ended maybe, and corrects course later if it has to. The clock is compressing a decision that would normally take longer.', 'An instant lurch in the stomach, resolving into anxious spiral — that keeps resurfacing in quiet moments for days afterward.', 0.47, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('5b4f16f1-1a2f-4f89-a077-e18276647421', '39073642-6f0a-4705-a163-c7c6d8e92b7e', '7b6f37f5-c76e-46ea-8169-21f32e56ec9c', 'Faced with this, this person waits for authorization even when it costs time, unwilling to freelance the response, and true to form assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.', 'Revisits the same decision from a new angle each time doubt resurfaces, even after nominally deciding. The clock is compressing a decision that would normally take longer.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into stoic freeze — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.65, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
