('a26e4690-d9df-422b-9b69-f3f08e7fdda9', 'b244bccd-aef5-4204-a030-9b8c524ca1fc', '6e8faf55-b16b-45db-9c19-4bfc369e23f1', 'Faced with this, this profile chooses the gentlest true version of events available, and true to form finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 'Feels most confident the moment someone with more authority confirms the direction, and shaky right up until then. The social cost and the practical cost point in different directions.', 'A quick surge of adrenaline that fades as fast as it came, resolving into aggressive counter — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.63, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('a7dbfbbe-b57c-4f26-8aed-8a0ad6be58b7', '739f05c7-798a-4745-9f39-607404445b6d', '94d6e28c-b84a-42d9-9625-63b40b2847a5', 'Faced with this, the individual stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form prices every token against its all-time high, viewing current levels as an automatic discount.', 'Walks every branch and contingency in sequence, uneasy until the residual ambiguity is as small as it can be. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into stoic freeze — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.73, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('3acfd302-b2d4-4fb4-99b7-45029e873676', 'c548601b-45ff-498b-8be1-b94b2d73b232', '7fa3857a-8ae5-479c-a7da-f1bc75f51a95', 'Faced with this, this profile acts on the first plausible fix without checking for a better one, and true to form refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.', 'Lets urgency substitute for analysis, converting pressure directly into action. There is no version of this where every stakeholder ends up satisfied.', 'A rush of adrenaline that narrows focus fast, resolving into dissociative deferral — that leaves a residue of vigilance well past the event itself.', 0.48, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('c741bb4b-8f87-4059-ac92-6026539ced1e', '37b52e64-921d-4e07-91d6-32a3f5dcc76a', '09012784-e9fd-4c1a-9bca-012c91055bcc', 'Faced with this, this person lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. The counterparty is reading every hesitation as information.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into fomo buying — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.62, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('5356e535-2981-4880-86a5-65a42dbe4c74', '0049d1e6-1164-4ea6-adb5-136f91950c4c', '3f16a2c2-b990-4db8-9f26-5f0e1df34dfb', 'Faced with this, this profile responds deliberately, choosing words to protect their standing without escalating, and true to form is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. Whatever happens next becomes part of the story people tell about it.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into stoic freeze — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.71, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('f79a7f41-27ae-42ae-86f6-1c048b22e2d4', '115a78b1-33a5-470a-a045-2977996473b3', '3f16a2c2-b990-4db8-9f26-5f0e1df34dfb', 'Faced with this, the individual responds deliberately, choosing words to protect their standing without escalating, and true to form underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. Whatever happens next becomes part of the story people tell about it.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into stoic freeze — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.85, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('9e65d560-c30c-4ca8-87a8-f32555593fdd', 'db78473b-7569-4583-a66e-f5cc1558e9bc', '4405e81d-9ffa-4b5c-91d0-66f442bad6b4', 'Faced with this, this person isolates the irreversible choices and makes those first, deferring the rest, and true to form discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. Getting this wrong in public is worse than getting it wrong quietly.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into performative calm — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.75, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('b7b4079c-78b9-4eb3-9615-8d374578eef6', 'c561d599-7f5a-41fc-8e0d-8d61805dbfca', '305b4f3b-20ea-4397-b2b3-9550b67d7bef', 'Faced with this, this person lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into performative calm — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.76, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('cb0bcfaa-b105-4959-81fc-fe1d5e038838', '5e6ad860-a2bd-46ff-a3db-67884fd05d2a', 'dfa72cc9-0ee3-4048-9e6d-d601bce43afb', 'Faced with this, this type calls it out publicly rather than let it pass unaddressed, and true to form discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 'Feels the decision settle before it is fully articulated, and moves on that settling rather than waiting for certainty. An audience is watching how this gets handled.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into vindication seeking — that fades within the hour once the decision is locked in.', 0.48, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('e81c1989-b282-4378-9534-64c7deb2e2fc', '5bb6f6b9-6ba2-4bb1-99a2-0f1205670950', 'dfa72cc9-0ee3-4048-9e6d-d601bce43afb', 'Faced with this, the individual steps back and lets the moment pass rather than force a resolution, and true to form measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value.', 'Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and resists pressure to shortcut the process. Whatever happens next becomes part of the story people tell about it.', 'A flash of heat that cools almost immediately, resolving into righteous anger — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.69, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('6e7868b7-3866-418f-b06c-fd2302fa28e9', '5d0f2c88-6daa-46f8-a38f-cd0d14756547', '5b22dd1d-712f-4728-883a-247c094d1f40', 'Faced with this, this profile runs the scenario through a checklist built in advance and follows wherever it points, and true to form extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 'Breaks the decision into weighted criteria before looking at gut feel, and lets the tally overrule any single strong reaction. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into stoic freeze — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.68, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('05caec2d-97a0-4bb0-ac0e-f9e3eee5db49', '5ca66f56-dff9-4559-b0a4-33651eb78b45', '428eedc0-a3a5-4f70-8c25-0ab71ee0a6be', 'Faced with this, this profile sets an ultimatum earlier than convention allows, betting the other side blinks first, and true to form cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.', 'Trusts the first workable idea enough to move on it before a second one can compete for attention. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A rush of adrenaline that narrows focus fast, resolving into guilt absorption — that keeps resurfacing in quiet moments for days afterward.', 0.56, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('f5c851b9-7ca1-45b1-81f0-421506ca8591', 'c1abdfa9-795a-4d00-8fec-d4b24a28083d', 'e63e489a-82eb-4702-bca0-30e3a6ff7bff', 'Faced with this, this profile reads the room fully before committing to a position, and true to form refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak.', 'Separates the emotional read from the analytical one on purpose, writes both down, and lets the analytical read win the tiebreak. An audience is watching how this gets handled.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into performative calm — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.77, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('26145b50-a9be-4845-b425-64de4db7d413', '1de7cfd8-d95f-4ea7-a3c9-071268caa8a1', '9d7a1ba1-c9d3-43db-9e8d-6d59411d80d3', 'Faced with this, this person frames the response so it can be walked back later if needed, and true to form refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. An audience is watching how this gets handled.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into performative calm — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.66, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('387ec3a3-ba09-4fd0-84b5-e74305dca35a', '960bb939-4143-4187-99b8-e8b66f49f5a0', 'dfa72cc9-0ee3-4048-9e6d-d601bce43afb', 'Faced with this, this type responds in the heat of it, unfiltered, and true to form exits winning positions at the first minor delay or quiet period from devs.', 'Feels the decision settle before it is fully articulated, and moves on that settling rather than waiting for certainty. An audience is watching how this gets handled.', 'An immediate jolt of alarm, resolving into dissociative deferral — that leaves a residue of vigilance well past the event itself.', 0.5, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('d43e5521-1c6f-474b-94c4-71b845314164', 'ea002320-da77-4d53-8366-a96fcd38af01', 'e1fdcaee-3b02-4815-aec1-be30f6877b6d', 'Faced with this, the individual treats the moment as one more data point for a system, not an exception to react to, and true to form holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 'Breaks the decision into weighted criteria before looking at gut feel, and lets the tally overrule any single strong reaction. Price action does not care which argument feels more convincing.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into euphoric overreach — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.86, '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c')
